(22, 65, 'Degrees - old', 'degree-old', '<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Master\'s Programs</strong></h1>\r\n<p><strong>MA Animation</strong></p>\r\n<p>Provides a combination of artistic and technical training that prepares students for a future in 3D character animation, computer game art, or visual effects.</p>\r\n<p><a title=\"MA in Animation\" href=\"http://www.cdm.depaul.edu/academics/Pages/MA-in-Animation.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">About the MA in Animation Program</a></p>\r\n<p>Curriculum and Requirements</p>\r\n<p><a title=\"Animator Concentration\" href=\"http://www.cdm.depaul.edu/academics/Pages/Current/Requirements-MA-In-Animation-Animator.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Animator Concentration</a></p>\r\n<p><a title=\"Technical Artist\" href=\"http://www.cdm.depaul.edu/academics/Pages/Current/Requirements-MA-In-Animation-Technical-Artist.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Technical Artist</a></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><strong>MS Applied Technology</strong></p>\r\n<p>This is a joint degree with The School for New Learning for experienced IT professionals who wish to acquire advanced technical skills in a highly focused area, in combination with enhanced understanding of the larger organizational, economic, and social contexts within which these technical skills are practiced.</p>\r\n<p><a title=\"About the MS in Applied Technology Program\" href=\"http://www.cdm.depaul.edu/academics/Pages/MS_AppliedTechnology.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">About the MS in Applied Technology Program</a></p>\r\n<p><a title=\"Curriculum and Requirements\" href=\"http://www.cdm.depaul.edu/academics/Pages/Current/Requirements-MS-Applied-Technology.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Curriculum and Requirements</a></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><strong>MS Business Information Technology</strong></p>\r\n<p>Provides an understanding of the core principles for the management of information in corporations, health care institutions, and government agencies. Joint degree between CDM and The Kellstadt Graduate School of Business.</p>\r\n<p><a title=\"About the MS in Business Information Technology Program\" href=\"http://www.cdm.depaul.edu/academics/Pages/MSInBusinessInformationTechnology.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">About the MS in Business Information Technology Program</a></p>\r\n<p><a title=\"Curriculum and Requirements\" href=\"http://www.cdm.depaul.edu/academics/Pages/Current/Requirements-MS-In-Business-Information-Technology.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Curriculum and Requirements</a></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><strong>MS Computational Finance</strong></p>\r\n<p>Is a joint degree between CDM and the Kellstadt Graduate School of Business, offering students the skills to approach financial models through a quantitative framework. The program prepares students for careers in the field of quantitative financial analysis in areas including portfolio management, risk management, and financial engineering.</p>\r\n<p><a title=\"About the MS in Computational Finance Program\" href=\"http://www.cdm.depaul.edu/academics/Pages/MSInComputationalFinance.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">About the MS in Computational Finance Program</a></p>\r\n<p><a title=\"Curriculum and Requirements\" href=\"http://www.cdm.depaul.edu/academics/Pages/Current/Requirements-MS-In-Computational-Finance.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Curriculum and Requirements</a></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><strong>MS Computer Science</strong></p>\r\n<p>Exposes students to the complete life-cycle of computer application development including abstraction, modeling and algorithm development, leveraging computer systems, programming languages and development frameworks, and software development techniques and processes. It prepares students for a professional career in Software Development or Computer Science Research. </p>\r\n<p><a title=\"About the MS in Computer Science Program\" href=\"http://www.cdm.depaul.edu/academics/Pages/MSInComputerScience.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">About the MS in Computer Science Program</a></p>\r\n<p><a title=\"Curriculum and Requirements\" href=\"http://www.cdm.depaul.edu/academics/Pages/Current/Requirements-MS-in-Computer-Science.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Curriculum and Requirements</a></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><strong>MS Cybersecurity</strong></p>\r\n<p>Is intended for students who wish to specialize in the security aspects of Information Technology. Students will learn how to design, implement and maintain software systems designed to support security policy and network architecture consistent with mitigating risk and preventing hostile attacks. </p>\r\n<p><a title=\"About the MS in Cybersecurity Program\" href=\"http://www.cdm.depaul.edu/academics/Pages/MS-in-Cybersecurity.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">About the MS in Cybersecurity Program</a></p>\r\n<p>Curriculum and Requirements</p>\r\n<p><a title=\"Computer Security Concentration\" href=\"http://www.cdm.depaul.edu/academics/Pages/Current/Requirements-MS-in-Cybersecurity-Computer-Security.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Computer Security Concentration</a></p>\r\n<p><a title=\"Governance, Risk Management and Compliance Concentration\" href=\"http://www.cdm.depaul.edu/academics/Pages/Current/Requirements-MS-in-Cybersecurity-Compliance.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Governance, Risk Management and Compliance Concentration</a></p>\r\n<p><a title=\"Networking and Infrastructure Concentration\" href=\"http://www.cdm.depaul.edu/academics/Pages/Current/Requirements-MS-in-Cybersecurity-Networking-and-Infrastructure.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Networking and Infrastructure Concentration</a></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><strong>MA Digital Communication and Media Arts</strong></p>\r\n<p>Grounded in practice and theory, this degree teaches students how digital technology has affected communication and artistic practices and how to affect future change through the integration of digital technology. This is a joint degree with the College of Communication. </p>\r\n<p><a title=\"About the MA in Digital Communication and Media Arts Program\" href=\"http://www.cdm.depaul.edu/academics/Pages/MAInDCMA.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">About the MA in Digital Communication and Media Arts Program</a></p>\r\n<p><a title=\"Curriculum and Requirements\" href=\"http://www.cdm.depaul.edu/academics/Pages/Current/Requirements-MA-in-Digital-Communication-and-Media-Arts.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Curriculum and Requirements</a></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><strong>MS E-Commerce Technology</strong></p>\r\n<p>Is designed for those who want to specialize in e-business systems development and management. The program provides flexible, modularized advanced training in e-business systems as well as competencies in Internet application development, advanced Internet technologies, and wireless applications.</p>\r\n<p><a title=\"About the MS in E-Commerce Technology Program\" href=\"http://www.cdm.depaul.edu/academics/Pages/MSEcommerceTechnology.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">About the MS in E-Commerce Technology Program</a></p>\r\n<p><a title=\"Curriculum and Requirements\" href=\"http://www.cdm.depaul.edu/academics/Pages/Current/Requirements-MS-E-Commerce-Technology.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Curriculum and Requirements</a></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><strong>MA Experience Design</strong></p>\r\n<p>Addresses the growing demand for professionals with a combination of skills to effectively design processes, services, events, and environments with a focus placed on the quality of the user experience and culturally relevant solutions. </p>\r\n<p><a title=\"About the MA in Experience Design Program\" href=\"http://www.cdm.depaul.edu/academics/Pages/MA-In-Experience-Design.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">About the MA in Experience Design Program</a></p>\r\n<p><a title=\"Curriculum and Requirements\" href=\"http://www.cdm.depaul.edu/academics/Pages/Current/Requirements-MA-in-Experience-Design.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Curriculum and Requirements</a></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><strong>MS Film and Television</strong></p>\r\n<p>Emphasizes the technical and technology-based topics and practices of digital cinema. Such topics and practices include post-production editing of video and audio, the integration of video and audio, special effects and computer-generated imaging, and modes of digital distribution.</p>\r\n<p><a title=\"About the MS in Film and Television Program\" href=\"http://www.cdm.depaul.edu/academics/Pages/MS-in-Film-and-Television.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">About the MS in Film and Television Program</a></p>\r\n<p>Curriculum and Requirements</p>\r\n<p><a title=\"Cinematography Concentration\" href=\"http://www.cdm.depaul.edu/academics/Pages/Current/Requirements-MS-in-Film-and-Television-Cinematography.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Cinematography Concentration</a></p>\r\n<p><a title=\"Post-Production Concentration\" href=\"http://www.cdm.depaul.edu/academics/Pages/Current/Requirements-MS-in-Film-and-Television-Post-Production.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Post-Production Concentration</a></p>\r\n<p><a title=\"Sound Concentration\" href=\"http://www.cdm.depaul.edu/academics/Pages/Current/Requirements-MS-in-Film-and-Television-Sound.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Sound Concentration</a></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><strong>MS Game Programming</strong></p>\r\n<p>Is designed for those interested in game development programming at the highest level, including computer science and computer graphics professionals retooling for the game industry.</p>\r\n<p><a title=\"About the MS in Game Programming Program\" href=\"http://www.cdm.depaul.edu/academics/Pages/MS-in-Game-Programming.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">About the MS in Game Programming Program</a></p>\r\n<p><a title=\"Curriculum and Requirements\" href=\"http://www.cdm.depaul.edu/academics/Pages/Current/Requirements-MS-In-Game-Programming.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Curriculum and Requirements</a></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><strong>MS Health Informatics</strong></p>\r\n<p>Provides students with the skills and knowledge needed to implement and support information technology solutions for health sector organizations.</p>\r\n<p><a title=\"About the MS in Health Informatics Program\" href=\"http://www.cdm.depaul.edu/academics/Pages/MSinHealthInformatics.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">About the MS in Health Informatics Program</a></p>\r\n<p><a title=\"Curriculum and Requirements\" href=\"http://www.cdm.depaul.edu/academics/Pages/Current/Requirements-MS-In-Health-Informatics.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Curriculum and Requirements</a></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><strong>MS Human-Computer Interaction</strong></p>\r\n<p>Focuses on the design, implementation, and evaluation of computer interfaces that are accessible and easy for people to use.</p>\r\n<p><a title=\"About the MS in Human-Computer Interaction Program\" href=\"http://www.cdm.depaul.edu/academics/Pages/MSInHuman-ComputerInteraction.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">About the MS in Human-Computer Interaction Program</a></p>\r\n<p><a title=\"Curriculum and Requirements\" href=\"http://www.cdm.depaul.edu/academics/Pages/Current/Requirements-MS-in-Human-Computer-Interaction.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Curriculum and Requirements</a></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><strong>MS Information Systems</strong></p>\r\n<p>Focuses on the planning, development and management of information systems that enable organizations to gain strategic and tactical competitive advantage.</p>\r\n<p><a title=\"About the MS in Information Systems Program\" href=\"http://www.cdm.depaul.edu/academics/Pages/MSInInformationSystems.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">About the MS in Information Systems Program</a></p>\r\n<p>Curriculum and Requirements</p>\r\n<p><a title=\"Business Analysis/Systems Analysis Concentration\" href=\"http://www.cdm.depaul.edu/academics/Pages/Current/Requirements-MS-IS-Business-Systems-Analysis.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Business Analysis/Systems Analysis Concentration</a></p>\r\n<p><a title=\"Business Intelligence Concentration\" href=\"http://www.cdm.depaul.edu/academics/Pages/Current/Requirements-MS-IS-Business-Intelligence.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Business Intelligence Concentration</a></p>\r\n<p><a title=\"Database Administration Concentration\" href=\"http://www.cdm.depaul.edu/academics/Pages/Current/Requirements-MS-IS-Database-Administration.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Database Administration Concentration</a></p>\r\n<p><a title=\"IT Enterprise Management Concentration\" href=\"http://www.cdm.depaul.edu/academics/Pages/Current/Requirements-MS-IS-IT-Enterprise-Management.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">IT Enterprise Management Concentration</a></p>\r\n<p><a title=\"Standard Concentration\" href=\"http://www.cdm.depaul.edu/academics/Pages/Current/Requirements-MS-IS-Standard.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Standard Concentration</a></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><strong>MS IT Project Management</strong></p>\r\n<p>Prepares students for careers leading and managing IT project teams by providing in-depth knowledge of project management skills including risk management, procurement and contract management, time and cost estimating, IT testing, quality assurance, and control.</p>\r\n<p><a title=\"About the MS in IT Project Management Program\" href=\"http://www.cdm.depaul.edu/academics/Pages/MSInITProjectManagement.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">About the MS in IT Project Management Program</a></p>\r\n<p><a title=\"Curriculum and Requirements\" href=\"http://www.cdm.depaul.edu/academics/Pages/Current/Requirements-MS-in-IT-Project-Management.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Curriculum and Requirements</a></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><strong>MS Network Engineering and Security</strong></p>\r\n<p>Trains professionals who meet current industry demands for innovative network designs, and the development of new network applications and services for business enterprises and the network providers that serve them. This program offers theoretical and applied study of the design, configuration and management of converged communication networks</p>\r\n<p><a title=\"About the MS in Network Engineering and Security Program\" href=\"http://www.cdm.depaul.edu/academics/Pages/MSInNetworkEngineeringandManagement.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">About the MS in Network Engineering and Security Program</a></p>\r\n<p><a title=\"Curriculum and Requirements\" href=\"http://www.cdm.depaul.edu/academics/Pages/Current/Requirements-MS-in-Network-Engineering-and-Security.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Curriculum and Requirements</a></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><strong>MS Predictive Analytics</strong></p>\r\n<p>Graduates of this program will obtain a variety of skills required for a career in predictive analytics, including the ability to analyze large datasets and to develop modeling solutions to support decision making, a good understanding of the fundamental principles of marketing and customer relationship management, and communication skills to present results effectively to a non-technical business audience. The program aims to prepare students with the required qualifications to become data mining analysts/engineers or predictive modelers.</p>\r\n<p><a title=\"About the MS in Predictive Analytics Program\" href=\"http://www.cdm.depaul.edu/academics/Pages/MS-in-Predictive-Analytics.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">About the MS in Predictive Analytics Program</a></p>\r\n<p>Curriculum and Requirements</p>\r\n<p><a title=\"Computational Methods Concentration\" href=\"http://www.cdm.depaul.edu/academics/Pages/Current/Requirements-MS-In-Predictive-Analytics-Computational.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Computational Methods Concentration</a></p>\r\n<p><a title=\"Health Care Concentration\" href=\"http://www.cdm.depaul.edu/academics/Pages/Current/Requirements-MS-In-Predictive-Analytics-Health-Care.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Health Care Concentration</a></p>\r\n<p><a title=\"Hospitality Concentration\" href=\"http://www.cdm.depaul.edu/academics/Pages/Current/Requirements-MS-in-Predictive-Analytics-Hospitality.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Hospitality Concentration</a></p>\r\n<p><a title=\"Marketing Concentration\" href=\"http://www.cdm.depaul.edu/academics/Pages/Current/Requirements-MS-In-Predictive-Analytics-Marketing.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Marketing Concentration</a></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><strong>MS Software Engineering</strong></p>\r\n<p>Provides students with marketable skills in methodologies, techniques, and tools of software engineering. The program encompasses the entire life-cycle of software development including requirements, analysis, design, construction, testing, and project management. Emphasis is placed on current and emerging technologies for engineering large and complex distributed software systems. According to the US Bureau of Labor Statistics, software engineer has been among the fastest growing IT professions in the US.</p>\r\n<p><a title=\"About the MS in Software Engineering Program\" href=\"http://www.cdm.depaul.edu/academics/Pages/MSInSoftwareEngineering.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">About the MS in Software Engineering Program</a></p>\r\n<p>Curriculum and Requirements</p>\r\n<p><a title=\"Entrepreneurship &amp; Technology Leadership Concentration\" href=\"http://www.cdm.depaul.edu/academics/Pages/Current/Requirements-MS-SE-Entrepreneurship.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Entrepreneurship &amp; Technology Leadership Concentration</a></p>\r\n<p><a title=\"Real-Time Game Systems Concentration\" href=\"http://www.cdm.depaul.edu/academics/Pages/Current/Requirements-MS-SE-Real-Time-Game-Systems.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Real-Time Game Systems Concentration</a></p>\r\n<p><a title=\"Software Architecture Concentration\" href=\"http://www.cdm.depaul.edu/academics/Pages/Current/Requirements-MS-SE-Software-Architecture.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Software Architecture Concentration</a></p>\r\n<p><a title=\"Software Development Concentration\" href=\"http://www.cdm.depaul.edu/academics/Pages/Current/Requirements-MS-SE-Software-Development.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Software Development Concentration</a></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><strong>JD/MS Computer Science Technology</strong></p>\r\n<p>Offers currently enrolled first year law students preparing for careers in intellectual property, in general practice with clients in IT, as in-house counsel in the IT industry, or in government agencies dealing with IT regulation opportunity to obtain an MS demonstrating proficiency in a focused area of Computer Science or Information Technology with only one additional year of coursework. Joint Degree between the College of Law Center for Intellectual Property Law &amp; Information Technology and CDM. </p>\r\n<p><a title=\"Curriculum and Requirements\" href=\"http://www.cdm.depaul.edu/academics/Pages/Current/Requirements-jdms-joint-degree.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Curriculum and Requirements</a></p>\r\n<p> </p>', '', 1, 11, '2013-09-16 14:29:56', 541, '', '2017-11-20 07:32:24', 541, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2013-09-16 14:29:56', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '{\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}', 16, 1, '', '', 1, 366, '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0, '*', ''),
